snippet.title: The Stand 2020 - The Cinema Snob
snippet.description:
Stephen King's The Stand has been adapted again in this 2020-2021 miniseries!  The Cinema Snob reviews the new show and sees how it compares to the 1994 version.

Writer/Creator: Brad Jones 
Title Card: Shaun Millington 

End Screen: Nick Michalak, http://www.ravensfilm.com

Music: Karl Casey at White Bat Audio 
Devin LeTroy Powell, Rhymer-Man, check out the full song:
https://youtu.be/MvA4URGP3pA
